Package: openNCAI
Type: Package
Title: Calculates a Natural Capital Assets Index
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-05-04
Authors@R: person(given = "Kate",
                      family = "O\'Hara",
                      role = c("aut", "cre"),
                      email = "k.a.ohara@stir.ac.uk")
Description: Calculates a regional natural capital assets index (NCAI) following
    the methodology designed by 'NatureScot' for 'Scotland'. Processes habitat 
    extent and condition data alongside metadata and weighting systems to 
    produce a yearly single figure indexed relative to a base-year value of 100.
